This directory contains some examples on how to use MailListStat.

File            Description
~~~~            ~~~~~~~~~~~
example.php     Simple example showing usage of PHP wrapper class
forward         Running MLS from your .forward file
procmailrc      Example of integration MLS with procmail

If you have integrated MailListStat with other software (like mailing list
managers) and would like to contribute, please send all your modifications,
config files, etc. to marki@nexin.sk
THANKS.
